### ✅ 정상 요청
POST http://localhost:3000/filterDomain
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "domain": "example.com",
  "emails": ["alice@example.com", "bob@test.com"]
}

### 🔥 악의적 요청
POST http://localhost:3000/filterDomain
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "domain": ".*(a+)+",
  "emails": ["attacker@.*(a+)+", "normal@domain.com"]
}
